data.description:
If you are looking for a move-in-ready home surrounded by a strong sense of community, we have found your match.  When asked what they would miss most when they move, the Sellers quickly answered ''The People''.  Located in the gated community of The Preserve at Hobe Sound and situated at the edge of the nature preserve, this could be the perfect place for YOU!  As you walk in the foyer, you will immediately feel the pride of ownership with the thoughtful details such as shiplap accent walls and built-in electric fireplace with mantle.  Granite kitchen with ample cabinet storage and counter space, as well as a breakfast nook for informal dining.  Step out the back sliders onto your covered and screened patio with vinyl windows.  Sip your coffee while enjoying nature and the preserve view. The community has miles of sidewalks with stunning views for your evening strolls.  When you pull in to the community entrance, be sure to stop and see the waterfalls on the right side!  This is a pet-friendly community, but no aggressive beed (pitbull/terriers and the like).  No weight restrictions and 2 dog maximum.  There are vehicle restrictions, so please refer to the community rules and regulations for verification.  

Flat tile roof was installed in 2012 and the home has complete IMPACT windows, doors, and skylights (with the exception of the front French doors, which have accordion shutters).  The kitchen appliances were updated in 2017 and the A/C was updated in 2020 to include an ultraviolet germicidal light.  

So many more features, but you'll need to book a showing to see for yourself!
